OL,3,CMan arrested after Glider staff member
OL,4,Cthreatened with Stanley knife
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a Glider
OL,7,Fstaff member was threatened with a
OL,8,FStanley knife.
OL,10,FThe incident happened in the Divis
OL,11,FStreet area of west Belfast on Friday.
OL,13,FA police spokesman said officers
OL,14,Freceived a report shortly after 9.30pm
OL,15,Fthat a man who had been travelling on
OL,16,Fa Glider became aggressive towards a
OL,17,Fmale staff member, before lunging at
OL,18,Fhim with a Stanley knife, and
OL,19,Fthreatening him.
