OL,6,F"The suspect, who is aged in his 20s,
OL,7,Fwas subsequently arrested by police on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of common assault and
OL,9,Fpossession of an offensive weapon in a
OL,10,Fpublic place," they said.
OL,12,F"He remains in police custody at this
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,15,FThe spokesman added: "Any assault is
OL,16,Fcompletely unacceptable, but an attack
OL,17,Fon a member of staff who is assisting
OL,18,Fthe local community is absolutely
OL,19,Fabhorrent.
